name: Vitamin E Oil Face & Body Moisturizer 4oz
description: Give your skin a nourishing boost with Vitamin E Oil Face and Body Moisturizer. This ultra-hydrating, antioxidant rich formula helps protect the skin from visible signs of aging while delivering powerful moisture that soothes and softens. A few drops can be used in the morning and night, applied to lightly damp skin after cleansing and toning for face, or throughout the body for an all-over dose of rejuvenation. Vitamin E is an essential ingredient, known for its natural antioxidant power that combats free radicals as it hydrates your skin. Ideal for all skin types, this vitamin-packed moisturizer makes the skin glow from within - make our Vitamin E Oil part of your everyday skincare routine! Ingredients: Glycine Soja (Soybean) Oil, Helianthusannus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Tocopheryl Acetate, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Oil.
